<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="sleepy-adj">sleepy <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'sliːpi/    美 /'sliːpi/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>困的；欲睡的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>feel / look sleepy
觉得/看起来困了</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.<strong>(城镇或地区) 冷清的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a sleepy village
冷清的村庄</p></div></div>